            ['name' => 'Jamaica', 'description' => 'Jamaica is a Caribbean island famous for reggae music, tropical beaches, and lush landscapes.', 'big_description' => 'Jamaica, covering 10,991 km² with a population of about 3 million, is a Caribbean island nation known for reggae music, Blue Mountains, tropical beaches, and vibrant culture. Kingston, the capital, is a hub of music and history. Jamaican traditions, cuisine, and festivals reflect African and European influences. Its lush landscapes, turquoise waters, and cultural richness make Jamaica a popular destination for tourism and cultural exploration.', 'image' => 'https://flagcdn.com/w320/jm.png', 'continent_id' => $north_america->id],
